<A NAME="Toolbar"><H2>Using the Toolbar</H2></A>
<P>The word processor toolbar contains several icons you can click on to access these options.  <B>Note: </B>Toolbar options noted with * are not displayed if you are using a television monitor with your NC.  

<UL>
<TABLE BORDER = 0><TR><TD>
<IMG WIDTH=25 HEIGHT=25 SRC="icontype:nc_vmenu"><TD><B>Menu</B> displays the following menu options:<TR><TD>
<TD><B>Document</B> displays these options: change title, save and print.<TR><TD>
<TD><B>Edit</B> displays these editing options: Undo, Cut, Copy, Paste, Start selection, Select all and Select paragraph.<TR><TD>
<TD><B>Font</B> allows you to set the typeface used.<TR><TD>
<TD><B>Font size</B> allows you to set the size of the current font.<TR><TD>
<TD><B>Font color</B> allows you to set the color of the current font.<TR><TD>
<TD><B>Font style</B> displays these font style options: Italic, Bold and Underline.<TR><TD>
<TD><B>Alignment</B> displays these alignment options: Left, Center, Right and Fully justify.<TR><TD>
<TD><B>View</B> allows you to change the size of current editing view.<TR><TD>
<TD><B>Close</B> allows you to quit the word processor.<TR><TD>
<IMG WIDTH=25 HEIGHT=25 SRC="icontype:nc_vsave"><TD><B>Save</B> saves the current document.<TR><TD>
<IMG WIDTH=25 HEIGHT=25 SRC="icontype:nc_vprnt">*<TD><B>Print</B> prints the current document.<TR><TD>
<IMG WIDTH=25 HEIGHT=25 SRC="icontype:nc_vundo">*<TD><B>Undo/Redo</B> reverses the most recent action.<TR><TD>
<IMG WIDTH=25 HEIGHT=25 SRC="icontype:nc_vcut"><TD><B>Cut</B> cuts the current selection to the clipboard.<TR><TD>
<IMG WIDTH=25 HEIGHT=25 SRC="icontype:nc_vcopy"><TD><B>Copy</B> copies the current selection to the clipboard.<TR><TD>
<IMG WIDTH=25 HEIGHT=25 SRC="icontype:nc_vpast"><TD><B>Paste</B> inserts the clipboard contents into the document.<TR><TD>
<IMG WIDTH=25 HEIGHT=25 SRC="icontype:nc_vbold"><TD><B>Bold</B> toggles bold style on/off.<TR><TD>
<IMG WIDTH=25 HEIGHT=25 SRC="icontype:nc_vital"><TD><B>Italic</B> toggles italic style on/off.<TR><TD>
<IMG WIDTH=25 HEIGHT=25 SRC="icontype:nc_vunde">*<TD><B>Underline</B> toggles underline style on/off.<TR><TD>
<IMG WIDTH=25 HEIGHT=13 SRC="icontype:nc_vzup"><TD><B>Zoom Up</B> increases the size of the editing view.<TR><TD>
<IMG WIDTH=25 HEIGHT=13 SRC="icontype:nc_vzdow"><TD><B>Zoom Down</B> decreases the size of the editing view.<TR><TD>
<IMG WIDTH=25 HEIGHT=25 SRC="icontype:nc_vhelp"><TD><B>Help</B> displays this help screen.<TR><TD>
<IMG WIDTH=15 HEIGHT=11 SRC="icontype:nc_vup"><IMG WIDTH=15 HEIGHT=11 SRC="icontype:nc_vdown"><TD><B>Page Up/Down</B> moves up/down one screen.<TR><TD>
<IMG WIDTH=15 HEIGHT=11 SRC="icontype:nc_vleft"><IMG WIDTH=15 HEIGHT=11 SRC="icontype:nc_vright"><TD><B>Page Left/Right</B> move left/right one screen.<TR><TD>
<IMG WIDTH=25 HEIGHT=25 SRC="icontype:nc_vclos"><TD><B>Close</B> quits the word processor.<TR><TD>
</TABLE></UL>

