<H2><A NAME="Keyboard">Using the Keyboard</A></H2>
<P>You can use the following keyboard shortcuts with the word processor:<P> 

<UL>
<TABLE BORDER=2 CELLPADDING=4><TR>
<TH>Function  </TH><TH>  Key</TH></TR>
<TR><TD>Display Help</TD><TD>F1</TD></TR>
<TR><TD>Display Menu</TD><TD>F2</TD></TR>
<TR><TD>Toggle Toolbar on/off</TD><TD>F12</TD></TR>
<TR><TD>Save</TD><TD>Ctrl+S</TD></TR>
<TR><TD>Undo/Redo</TD><TD>Ctrl+Z</TD></TR>
<TR><TD>Print</TD><TD>Ctrl+P</TD></TR>
<TR><TD>Cut</TD><TD>Ctrl+X</TD></TR>
<TR><TD>Copy</TD><TD>Ctrl+C</TD></TR>
<TR><TD>Paste</TD><TD>Ctrl+V</TD></TR>
<TR><TD>Select all</TD><TD>Ctrl+A</TD></TR>
<TR><TD>Bold</TD><TD>Ctrl+B</TD></TR>
<TR><TD>Italic</TD><TD>Ctrl+I</TD></TR>
<TR><TD>Underline</TD><TD>Ctrl+U</TD></TR>
</TABLE></UL><P>

